==English==

===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|weyfaren}}, originally in participle form {{m|enm|weyfarand}}, from {{der|en|ang|weġfarende||wayfaring}}, equivalent to {{compound|en|way|faring}}. Cognate with {{cog|da|vejfarende||wayfaring}}, {{cog|sv|vägfarande|}}, {{cog|de|wegfahren||to drive away}}, {{cog|is|vegfarandi||wayfaring}}. More at {{l|en|way}}, {{l|en|fare}}.

